5.1. Vit hm (khng s dng th vin) :

a. Lt ngang nh

In[]:
def flip_image_horizontally(image):
    rows, cols, channels = image.shape
    flipped_image = np.zeros((rows, cols, channels), dtype=np.uint8)
    
    for row in range(rows):
        for col in range(cols):
            flipped_image[row, col] = image[row, cols - col - 1]
    
    return flipped_image

hor = flip_image_horizontally(img)

b. Lt nh theo chiu dc

In[]:
def flip_image_vertically(image):
    rows, cols, channels = image.shape
    flipped_image = np.zeros((rows, cols, channels), dtype=np.uint8)
    
    for row in range(rows):
        flipped_image[row] = image[rows - row - 1]
    
    return flipped_image

ver = flip_image_vertically(img)

c. Tnh tin nh sang phi v xung di 30 pixels mi chiu

In[]:
def translate_image(image, dx, dy):
    rows, cols, channels = image.shape
    translated_image = np.zeros((rows, cols, channels), dtype=np.uint8)
    
    for row in range(rows):
        for col in range(cols):
            new_row = row + dy
            new_col = col + dx
            
            if new_row < rows and new_col < cols:
                translated_image[new_row, new_col] = image[row, col]
    
    return translated_image

trans = translate_image(img, 30, 30)

d. Xoay nh 30 theo chiu kim ng h

In[]:
def rotate_image(image, angle):
    angle_rad = np.radians(angle)
    rows, cols, channels = image.shape
    rotated_image = np.zeros((rows, cols, channels), dtype=np.uint8)
    center_row = int(rows / 2)
    center_col = int(cols / 2)
    
    for row in range(rows):
        for col in range(cols):
            x = col - center_col
            y = row - center_row
            new_x = int(x * np.cos(angle_rad) + y * np.sin(angle_rad)) + center_col
            new_y = int(-x * np.sin(angle_rad) + y * np.cos(angle_rad)) + center_row
            
            if 0 <= new_x < cols and 0 <= new_y < rows:
                rotated_image[new_y, new_x] = image[row, col]
    
    return rotated_image

rot = rotate_image(img, -30)

e. Scale nh xung cn 1/2 mi chiu

In[]:
def scale_image(image, scale):
    rows, cols, channels = image.shape
    scaled_rows = int(rows / scale)
    scaled_cols = int(cols / scale)
    scaled_image = np.zeros((scaled_rows, scaled_cols, channels), dtype=np.uint8)
    
    for row in range(scaled_rows):
        for col in range(scaled_cols):
            scaled_image[row, col] = image[row*scale, col*scale]
    
    return scaled_image

scl = scale_image(img, 2)

So snh kt qu gia nh gc v nh sau khi bin i

for i in range(columns*rows):
    ax[i // columns, i % columns].imshow(img_list[i])
    ax[i // columns, i % columns].set_title(titles[i])
plt.tight_layout()

    return flipped_image

c. Tnh tin nh sang phi v xung di 30 pixels mi chiu

In[]:
def translate_image2(image, dx, dy):
    rows, cols, _ = image.shape
    M = np.float32([[1, 0, dx], [0, 1, dy]])    #Ma trn tnh tin
    translated_image = cv2.warpAffine(img, M, (cols, rows))
    return translated_image

trans2 = translate_image2(img, 30, 30)

d. Xoay nh 30 theo chiu kim ng h

In[]:
def rotate_image2(image, angle):
    height, width = image.shape[:2]
    center = (width // 2, height // 2)  # Tnh ton ma trn xoay
    scale = 1.0
    M = cv2.getRotationMatrix2D(center, angle, scale)
    rotated_image = cv2.warpAffine(image, M, (width, height))
    return rotated_image

rot2 = rotate_image2(img, -30)

e. Scale nh xung cn 1/2 mi chiu

In[]:
def scale_image2(image, scale):
    rows, cols, _ = image.shape
    scaled_rows = int(rows / scale)
    scaled_cols = int(cols / scale)
    scaled_image = cv2.resize(image, (scaled_rows, scaled_cols))
    return scaled_image

scl2 = scale_image2(img, 2)

5.3. Scale nh cn 1/8 mi chiu so vi ban u, sau scale nh kt qu ln 8 ln mi chiu. So snh nh gc v nh cui

Scale nh gc 1/8 mi chiu, sau scale nh kt qu 8 ln mi chiu, thu c nh cui

In[]:
scale_step = scale_image2(img, 8)
scale_end = scale_image2(scale_step, 1/8)

So snh 2 nh gc v nh scale cui:

nh gc r hn nh scale cui. Khi scale nh xung, tc l gim kch thc ca nh v lm mt i mt s chi tit nh. Khi scale ln li, phi tng kch thc ca nh v gp kh khn trong vic ti to cc chi tit b mt. Qu trnh ti to ny c th gy ra hin tng m hoc mt mt cht lng trong hnh nh.

Ngoi ra, qu trnh scale nh cng c th gy ra hin tng m do php ton trung bnh hoc ni suy dng in vo cc pixel mi trong qu trnh scale. Cch x l ny c th gy mt mt sc nt v to ra hin tng m trong hnh nh.
